China to Start Carbon Emissons Trading Trials, Xinhua Reports

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-07-17T23:11:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-17/china-to-start-carbon-emissons-trading-trials-xinhua-reports.html
China  will start trials of carbon
emission trading and gradually set up a carbon emissions trading
market, the official Xinhua News Agency reported yesterday,
citing National Development and Reform Commission Vice Minister
 Xie Zhenhua .  The government will also accelerate the building of an
energy saving and environmental protection system, and tighten
regulations for identifying and labeling low-carbon products,
Xinhua cited Xie as saying.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
 jliu42@bloomberg.net  